            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1897.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>, add 1/4 of your<strong> grated cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to the tray, and form into a long rectangular shape</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 7-8 min or until the cheese has completely melted and is starting to brown</p><p>Once melted, remove the tray from the oven and set aside to cool</p><p>Once cooled, snap into 1 equal sized piece per person – these are your<strong> cheese tuiles</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1897.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1897.-step-6-x400.jpg",
