            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, remove the pan from the heat</p><p>Stir in <strong>half</strong> your<strong> truffle oil </strong>(save the rest for later!), the <strong>remaining grated cheese</strong> and a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> – this is your <strong>truffled mushroom risotto</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1897.-step-7-x200.jpg",
