          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1897.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> truffled mushroom risotto</strong> topped with the <strong>thyme-roasted portobellos</strong> and <strong>crushed hazelnuts</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>remaining truffle oil</strong> and top with a<strong> cheese tuile</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
